{"tha-ap97:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap97:0.2":"Sudhavagga ","tha-ap97:0.3":"Gandhamaliyattheraapadana ","tha-ap97:1.1":"“Siddhatthassa bhagavato, ","tha-ap97:1.2":"gandhathupam akasaham; ","tha-ap97:1.3":"Sumanehi paticchannam, ","tha-ap97:1.4":"buddhanucchavikam katam. ","tha-ap97:2.1":"Kancanagghiyasankasam, ","tha-ap97:2.2":"buddham lokagganayakam; ","tha-ap97:2.3":"Indivaramva jalitam, ","tha-ap97:2.4":"adittamva hutasanam. ","tha-ap97:3.1":"Byagghusabhamva pavaram, ","tha-ap97:3.2":"abhijatamva kesarim; ","tha-ap97:3.3":"Nisinnam samananaggam, ","tha-ap97:3.4":"bhikkhusanghapurakkhatam. ","tha-ap97:4.1":"Vanditva satthuno pade, ","tha-ap97:4.2":"pakkamim uttaramukho; ","tha-ap97:4.3":"Catunnavutito kappe, ","tha-ap97:4.4":"gandhamalam yato adam. ","tha-ap97:5.1":"Buddhe katassa karassa, ","tha-ap97:5.2":"phalenaham visesato; ","tha-ap97:5.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap97:5.4":"buddhapujayidam phalam. ","tha-ap97:6.1":"Cattarisamhi ekune, ","tha-ap97:6.2":"kappe asimsu solasa; ","tha-ap97:6.3":"Devagandhasanama te, ","tha-ap97:6.4":"rajano cakkavattino. ","tha-ap97:7.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap97:7.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap97:7.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap97:8.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma gandhamaliyo thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap97:9.1":"Gandhamaliyattherassapadanam pancamam. "}